sub_title: Partner Happiness Manager France & Belgium Wallonia at Bambelo
summary:
With Bambelo, we bring supply and demand together on more than 25 quotation platforms in the Netherlands, Belgium, Spain, Italy, Germany and France. Consumers are looking for a service and on our platforms they are matched with professionals. 


As Happiness Manager, my goal is to help our partners achieve their business goals in a personal way. The Happiness Team supports partners in optimising marketing, business, lead and sales processes to achieve maximum returns. The partner's growth is key!
